            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My Son studying 9th std., Compare to all other schools, the SRMPS best in all aspects - Coaching (They are focusing not only on book learning and also on other aspects too like sports, music, business, speech training, physical and mental balancing activities includes yoga, library, Even during this pandemics time also their way of conducting online session its really awesome and excellent. its shows their experience and capability to plan and bring the same to children world. Everywhere there may be some cons, Meeting officials, refunding, etc., We should have some patience and consider the people working over there also as a human being, then there wont be any issues. Now due to this government oral communication we are facing 2nd and 3rd language issues, we changed thrice and switching between tamil-hindi-sanskrit. Rest is fine. GO AHEAD.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
